{
  "id": "adv_card_kkr_01_01",
  "title": "赤崎こころ",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_office-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "office-01-000-noon",
      "startTime": null
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_01_01-kkr001.m4a",
      "text": "あふ～っ……私だけ呼び出しって\nいったいなんのご用ですかぁ～～？",
      "startTime": 6.166666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_01_01-kkr002.m4a",
      "text": "昨日はライブでしたから、今日はリズノワは\n全員お休みのはず……ふぁ～～っ……すや～～",
      "startTime": 12.966666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_01_01-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "いやいや、疲れてるのは分かるけど起きてくれないか？\nこころに大事な話があるんだ",
      "startTime": 25.366666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_01_01-kkr003.m4a",
      "text": "ん～～むにゃむにゃ……莉央さん、もうパンケーキは\n食べられないですよぉ～～",
      "startTime": 33.7,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_01_01-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "熟睡しないでくれ。それと夢まで見ないでくれ\nこころに仕事のオファーが来てるんだ",
      "startTime": 40.733333333333334,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_01_01-kkr004.m4a",
      "text": "……ふぁっ、お仕事ですか？\nだったら、メンバー全員呼ばないと――はっ！？",
      "startTime": 45.53333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_01_01-kkr005.m4a",
      "text": "こころと二人きりになって\n今から何をするつもりですか～？",
      "startTime": 52.06666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_01_01-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "……え",
      "startTime": 55.333333333333336,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_01_01-kkr006.m4a",
      "text": "アレですか？　よくあるマネージャーが\nアイドルにやるヤツですか？",
      "startTime": 59.166666666666664,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_01_01-kkr007.m4a",
      "text": "仕事がほしいなら……分かってるね？　こころ",
      "startTime": 61.6,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_01_01-kkr008.m4a",
      "text": "ああっ、そんな\n{user}さん信じてたのに――",
      "startTime": 67.83333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_01_01-kkr009.m4a",
      "text": "いくら、こころが星見プロで一番可愛いからって……\nそんなエッチなこと、ファンが許しませんよ～",
      "startTime": 75.3,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_01_01-kkr010.m4a",
      "text": "そういうのは、こころはNGですから\n悪徳マネージャーにはお仕置きが必要ですね～？",
      "startTime": 81.6,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_01_01-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "いやいやいや\nそんなつもりは微塵もないから",
      "startTime": 86.36666666666666,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_01_01-kkr011.m4a",
      "text": "ホントですか～～？　でもこころは一番可愛いから\nつい魔が差したり……",
      "startTime": 92.76666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_01_01-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "俺は事務所の子は全員、同じくらい魅力的だと思ってる\n誰が一番とか、そういう気持ちはないよ",
      "startTime": 99.6,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_01_01-kkr012.m4a",
      "text": "え～～っ！？　そういう父親目線ではなく\n異性としてはタイプとかあるんじゃないですか？",
      "startTime": 106.53333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_01_01-kkr013.m4a",
      "text": "誰がタイプなんですか？\nあっ、もしかして年齢の近い莉央さんとか――",
      "startTime": 111.5,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_01_01-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "雑談はこのあたりにして、そろそろ仕事の話をしよう",
      "startTime": 116.46666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_01_01-kkr014.m4a",
      "text": "ちぇっ、{user}さんはノリが悪いですね～\nつまんないです",
      "startTime": 123.56666666666666,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_01_01-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "こころ単独でグラビアの話が来てるんだ",
      "startTime": 125.83333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_01_01-kkr015.m4a",
      "text": "ノリの悪いマネージャーって、こころは芸能関係者\nとしてどうかと思うんですけ――って、グラビアっ！？",
      "startTime": 132,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_01_01-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "そうだ、グラビア。青年誌のヤングミリオン",
      "startTime": 135.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_01_01-kkr016.m4a",
      "text": "超有名な雑誌じゃないですか！",
      "startTime": 140.23333333333332,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_01_01-koh009.m4a",
      "text": "――のウェブ版の特集記事",
      "startTime": 142.7,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_01_01-kkr017.m4a",
      "text": "え～っ、ウェブ版ですか～？\nてっきり、本誌の表紙も私かと思ったのに",
      "startTime": 148.1,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_01_01-koh010.m4a",
      "text": "いやいや、ウェブ版でも凄いことだよ\n大抜擢と言っていい",
      "startTime": 154.83333333333334,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_01_01-koh011.m4a",
      "text": "以前、そこの編集長と知り合いになったんだ\nそしたら、昨日話が来て――",
      "startTime": 160.03333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_01_01-kkr018.m4a",
      "text": "ふむふむ、ちゃんと仕事してますね\nこころは初めから出来る人だと思ってました",
      "startTime": 165.16666666666666,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_01_01-kkr019.m4a",
      "text": "あっ、髪にホコリが。よろしかったらお肩でも\nお揉みしましょうか？",
      "startTime": 171.66666666666666,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_01_01-koh012.m4a",
      "text": "さっきと態度が180度違うな……\nまあ、その腹黒キャラも君の魅力か",
      "startTime": 177.56666666666666,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_01_01-kkr020.m4a",
      "text": "腹黒だなんて、ひどいですよ～。こころは\n臨機応変に強いモノにすり寄ってるだけですから",
      "startTime": 184.20000000000002,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_01_01-koh013.m4a",
      "text": "分かった分かった。で、この話どうする？\n再来週が撮影で時間はあんまりないんだけど",
      "startTime": 193.56666666666666,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_01_01-kkr021.m4a",
      "text": "もちろん大丈夫ですよ\nライブの直後で、体も引き締まってますから",
      "startTime": 199.16666666666666,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_01_01-kkr022.m4a",
      "text": "ビキニでも、レオタードでも\n可憐に着こなしてみせます",
      "startTime": 203.86666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_01_01-koh014.m4a",
      "text": "衣装はステージ衣装だよ\nあくまでもパフォーマーとしての特集だから",
      "startTime": 208.06666666666666,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_01_01-kkr023.m4a",
      "text": "もちろんそっち系でも、こころのアイドルスマイルで\n読者のハートをがっちりわしづかみします！",
      "startTime": 214.36666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_01_01-koh015.m4a",
      "text": "分かった。じゃあ、先方には返事を出しておく\nお疲れ様、もう今日は帰ってもいいよ",
      "startTime": 221.93333333333334,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_01_01-kkr024.m4a",
